snippet.title: Skystrider | Demo Release
snippet.description:
THE DEMO IS HERE!

Skystrider is a 3-D Action Platformer. As a resurrected hero, explore a ruined world, navigating perilous paths amidst clouds and tides. Unleash ancient technology to open the way. 

Music and Audio Mixing - Greg Nicolett
Voice Over - Tim Alexander

🞛 Play the Demo on Steam NOW 🞛
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2434450/Skystrider/ 

🞛 Join our Discord 🞛
https://discord.gg/nNC2qqxR26

🞛 Follow us on Twitter and Instagram @ studioichor  🞛

Thanks to all those who've supported the team and the project so far!
